content.rendered:
AUTOMAX 4×4 is your one stop shop for 4wd accessories in coffs harbour

Automax 4X4 has an exceptional range of bullbars from leading suppliers such as Rhino 4X4, Rival by Drivetech, Rockarmor, AFN and is a fitting centre for many other brands. We can upgrade your suspension with the always popular Outback Armour, give you a lift with Boss Airbags, or the ultimate lift with The Ultimate Suspension.

Why not add bigger wheels with a wheel and tyre package and make your ultimate lift even higher. We have a large range of LED lightbars and spot lights on display thanks to Stedi, auto electrical services including Tow-Pro fitting and are now offering Roo Systems ECU remapping and exhaust systems.

Shop Online
